title: Episode 72 - Syngman Rhee
itunes:author: The History of the Cold War Podcast
itunes:summary: In this episode, we examine the life and the political career of Syngman Rhee the first president of South Korea. We look at his early life as a revolutionary,  his political leadership of South Korea during the early Cold War and his fall from power in 1960.
